articles.author: Jon Haworth
articles.title: Climber found dead after falling off highest peak in North America - ABC News
articles.description: Since 1980, at least 14 climbers have died in falls on the West Buttress route.
articles.content:
A climber has died at Denali National Park and Preserve in Alaska after park rangers found a body at an elevation of over three miles, officials said.
